  (paper "A3")
  (title_block
    (title "V-Cortex - Perifericos: GNSS, MicroSD, Expansao")
    (rev "v1.3")
    (company "V-Cortex")
    (comment 1 "Stage 5: NEO-M9N GNSS 10Hz + U.FL + Bias-T + supercap + PPS | Stage 6: MicroSD SPI + ESD + I2C")
    (comment 2 "NOVO: GNSS_PPS (GPIO35 via 100Ohm), Bias-T antena ativa (L_BIAS+C_BLOCK), decoupling completo")
    (comment 3 "CORRIGIDO v1.3: C_GNSS_10N LCSC C15849 era X7R (errado). Usar CC0402JRNPO9BN103 NP0 — verificar LCSC")
  )

  (lib_symbols)

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; BLOCO 1: GNSS NEO-M9N-00B + CIRCUITO COMPLETO
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "U_GNSS — u-blox NEO-M9N-00B\nMPN: NEO-M9N-00B | Sourcing: JLCPCB Global Sourcing ou consignment\nNAO disponivel na LCSC catalogo normal\nPackage: LGA-24 (6.0 x 6.0 x 1.0mm)\n*** SUPPLY CHAIN: cotar JLCPCB Global Sourcing antes de confirmar pedido ***\nAlternativa: comprar no Mouser/DigiKey e enviar como consignment ao JLCPCB\nDowngrade aceito: NEO-M8N-0-10 (geracao anterior, suporta 10Hz via UBX)\n\nALIMENTACAO:\n  VCC: +3.3V (modulo tem regulador interno; NEO-M9N-00B opera com VCC=3.3V)\n  VCC_IO: +3.3V (nivel logico das interfaces UART/I2C/SPI)\n  V_BCKP: supercap ASR-M-10-0.1F via diodo D_BAT + R_BAT\n\nINTERFACE UART:\n  UART_TX (NEO pino 5) -> GPIO16 ESP32 (GNSS_RX) @ 115200 baud\n  UART_RX (NEO pino 6) <- GPIO17 ESP32 (GNSS_TX) @ 115200 baud\n\nPPS — Pulse Per Second (GPIO35 ESP32):\n  TIMEPULSE (NEO pino 20) -> R_PPS(100Ohm) -> GPIO35 ESP32\n  LCSC R_PPS: C106232 (YAGEO RC0402FR-07100RL, 2.66M unid)\n  CORRIGIDO: C104 nao encontrado na LCSC\n\nDECOUPLING GNSS (3 niveis conforme Engineering Guide secao 3.3.2):\n  +3V3 -> [FB_GNSS 600Ohm] -> V_GNSS_VCC\n  V_GNSS_VCC -> C_GNSS_BULK(10uF) -> GND  (bulk)\n  V_GNSS_VCC -> C_GNSS_100N(100nF) -> GND (bypass, < 0.5mm do pino VCC)\n  V_GNSS_VCC -> C_GNSS_10N(10nF)  -> GND  (alta freq, < 0.5mm do pino VCC_IO)\n\n  COMPONENTES:\n  FB_GNSS:      BLM21PG601SN1D (LCSC: C41556732 muRata, 480 unid)\n                CORRIGIDO: C21179 nao encontrado\n  C_GNSS_BULK:  10uF X5R 0805 (LCSC: C96446)\n  C_GNSS_100N:  100nF X7R 0402 (LCSC: C14663)\n  C_GNSS_10N:   10nF C0G/NP0 0402 (LCSC: C3855387 muRata GRM1555C1E103JE01D, 25V, 16k unid)\n              *** CORRIGIDO v1.3: era C15849 X7R (ERRADO). C0G obrigatorio no VCC_IO ***\n              Nota: CC0402JRNPO9BN103 (Yageo) nao disponivel na LCSC — use C3855387"
    (at 20 20)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "15000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; BIAS-T PARA ANTENA ATIVA
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "BIAS-T — ALIMENTACAO ANTENA ATIVA GNSS\n(Engineering Guide secao 3.3.5)\n\nFUNCAO: fornece tensao DC ao cabo coaxial para alimentar o LNA\nda antena patch ativa via o mesmo cabo RF\n\nCIRCUITO:\n  V_GNSS_VCC (3.3V) ──[L_BIAS 47nH]──┬── RF+DC (ao conector U.FL)\n                                       │\n                                   [C_BLOCK 100pF NP0]── RF_IN do NEO-M9N\n\nCOMPONENTES:\n  L_BIAS:  47nH RF (LCSC: C2903684 Chilisin HP0603-47NH-N, 0603, 6945 unid)\n           FOOTPRINT: 0603 (nao 0402). Impedancia @ 1.575GHz ~ 465 Ohm\n           CORRIGIDO: Wurth 744777047A sem codigo LCSC valido\n  C_BLOCK: 100pF NP0 0402 (LCSC: C14858 Yageo, 4.65M unid)\n           NP0/C0G obrigatorio — estabilidade em RF 1575MHz\n\nSE ANTENA PASSIVA (patch sem LNA): omitir L_BIAS e C_BLOCK,\n  conectar NEO-M9N RF_IN diretamente a trilha 50Ohm ao U.FL"
    (at 20 300)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "15000002-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; SUPERCAP BACKUP GNSS
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "BAT1 — Supercap 0.1F/5.5V (Backup GNSS RTC)\n\nCIRCUITO:\n  +3V3 -> [D_BAT Schottky] -> [R_BAT 100Ohm] -> BAT1(0.1F/5.5V) -> GND\n                     │\n  V_BCKP NEO-M9N <───┘ (pino 14)\n\nD_BAT: 1N5819 SOD-323 (LCSC: C48997863 KTP, 204k unid)\n  CORRIGIDO: C8681 Vishay 1N5819WS sem estoque\n  Schottky 1A/40V, Vf~0.3V; V_BCKP ~ 3.0V (3.3V-0.3V)\n\nR_BAT: 100Ohm 1% 0402 (LCSC: C106232 YAGEO RC0402FR-07100RL)\n  CORRIGIDO: C104 nao encontrado na LCSC\n  Limita corrente de carga pico do supercap\n\nBAT1: 0.1F/5.5V SMD (LCSC: C6075487 Yezhan ASR-M-10-0.1F)\n  PACKAGE: 12.8 x 6mm — FOOTPRINT ALTERADO de 3.2x2.5 para 12.8x6mm\n  CPX3225A Seiko nao disponivel na LCSC\n  Alternativa menor se disponivel: C496056 (Yezhan ASR-M-2627)"
    (at 20 560)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "15000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; U.FL CONECTOR + TRILHA RF 50 OHM
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "J_ANT — Conector U.FL / IPEX SMD\nLCSC: C381116 (U.FL-R-SMT-1 Hirose, 1875 unid)\n\nTRILHA RF 50 OHM (CRITICA — ver LAYOUT_GUIDE.md):\n  Largura trilha: 0.34mm (50Ohm, stackup JLC04161H-7628, L1 ref GND L2, h~0.21mm)\n  Comprimento: < 10mm\n  Sem vias, sem 90 graus, clearance 1.0mm de outros sinais\n  Remover copper fill na regiao da trilha RF"
    (at 600 20)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "15000004-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; MICROSD — GPIO MAPPING CORRIGIDO
  ;; GPIO4=CS, GPIO13=MOSI, GPIO14=CLK, GPIO23=MISO
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "J_SD — Slot MicroSD Push-Push SMD\nLCSC: C52750848 (Minlenda MLD-TF PUSH-H18, 5970 unid)\nCORRIGIDO: C780928 XKB sem estoque\n\nPINAGEM SD em MODO SPI (GPIOs conforme Engineering Guide secao 2.2):\n  pino 1 (CS/DAT3):   SD_CS    <- GPIO4  ESP32 (pull-up R_SD_CS 10k)\n  pino 2 (CMD/MOSI):  SD_MOSI  <- GPIO13 ESP32\n  pino 3 (VSS):       GND\n  pino 4 (VDD):       +3V3 via C_SD_BULK\n  pino 5 (CLK):       SD_CLK   <- GPIO14 ESP32\n  pino 6 (VSS):       GND\n  pino 7 (DAT0/MISO): SD_MISO  -> GPIO23 ESP32\n\nDECOUPLING MicroSD:\n  C_SD_BULK: 10uF X5R 0805 (LCSC: C96446) — bulk VDD\n  C_SD_BYP:  100nF X7R 0402 (LCSC: C14663) — bypass VDD\n  R_SD_CS:   10k 0402 (LCSC: C60490 YAGEO RC0402FR-0710KL) — pull-up CS"
    (at 600 150)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "15000005-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; ESD + EXPANSAO I2C/GPIO
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "ESD PROTECAO HEADERS DE EXPANSAO:\n\nESD1, ESD2 — PRTR5V0U2X (LCSC: C53446675 NXP, 8695 unid)\n  2 canais ESD por pacote SOT-363, clamp 5.5V, cap 0.5pF\n\nHEADER I2C:\n  SDA (GPIO21) — pull-up R_I2C_SDA(4.7k) -> +3V3\n  SCL (GPIO22) — pull-up R_I2C_SCL(4.7k) -> +3V3\n  R_I2C_SDA: 4.7k 0402 (LCSC: C105871 YAGEO RC0402FR-074K7L, 2.4M unid)\n  R_I2C_SCL: 4.7k 0402 (LCSC: C105871)\n  CORRIGIDO: C25900 UNI-ROYAL 0402WGF4701TCE sem estoque"
    (at 600 470)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "15000006-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

  ;; ============================================================
  ;; RESUMO BOM — STAGES 5 e 6 — CODIGOS LCSC VERIFICADOS v1.3
  ;; ============================================================
  (text "RESUMO BOM — STAGE 5 (GNSS) e STAGE 6 (Perifericos) — rev v1.3\n\nREF           VALUE           LCSC          NOTAS\nU_GNSS        NEO-M9N-00B     GLOBAL_SRC    LGA-24, Global Sourcing ou consignment\nFB_GNSS       BLM21PG601SN1D  C41556732     Ferrite 600Ohm GNSS VCC (CORRIGIDO: C21179 NOT_FOUND)\nC_GNSS_BULK   10uF X5R        C96446        Bulk GNSS VCC\nC_GNSS_100N   100nF X7R       C14663        Bypass GNSS VCC\nC_GNSS_10N    10nF C0G        C3855387      muRata GRM1555C1E103JE01D 25V. CORRIGIDO v1.3: C15849 era X7R.\nL_BIAS        47nH RF 0603    C2903684      Bias-T antena ativa (Chilisin HP0603-47NH-N)\nC_BLOCK       100pF NP0       C14858        DC-block antena RF\nR_PPS         100Ohm          C106232       Serie GNSS PPS -> GPIO35 (CORRIGIDO: C104 NOT_FOUND)\nJ_ANT         U.FL            C381116       Conector antena externa\nD_BAT         1N5819          C48997863     Schottky carga supercap (CORRIGIDO: C8681 OUT)\nR_BAT         100Ohm          C106232       Limite corrente carga supercap\nBAT1          0.1F/5.5V SMD   C6075487      Supercap Yezhan 12.8x6mm (FOOTPRINT ALTERADO)\nJ_SD          MicroSD push    C52750848     Slot MicroSD Minlenda (CORRIGIDO: C780928 OUT)\nC_SD_BULK     10uF X5R        C96446        Bulk VDD SD\nC_SD_BYP      100nF X7R       C14663        Bypass VDD SD\nR_SD_CS       10k             C60490        Pull-up SD_CS (GPIO4)\nESD1          PRTR5V0U2X      C53446675     ESD 2 canais expansao 1\nESD2          PRTR5V0U2X      C53446675     ESD 2 canais expansao 2\nNTC1          10k B3950       C5221675      NTC Murata 0402 GPIO36 (Global Sourcing)\nR_NTC         10k             C60490        Pull-up NTC -> +3V3\nC_NTC         100nF           C14663        Filtro NTC ADC\nR_I2C_SDA     4.7k            C105871       Pull-up SDA GPIO21 (CORRIGIDO: C25900 OUT)\nR_I2C_SCL     4.7k            C105871       Pull-up SCL GPIO22"
    (at 20 780)
    (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "15000007-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

